This QPKG contains the source files of applications obtained/downloaded from the URLs shown below:

- OpenLDAP v2.4.23 
ftp://ftp.openldap.org/pub/OpenLDAP/openldap-release/openldap-2.4.23.tgz

Below's the configuration switch used to build each library as well as its source origin

- OpenLDAP v2.4.23

1) ./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc --localstatedir=/var --libexecdir=/usr/sbin --enable-modules --enable-ldap --enable-passwd --with-threads --with-odbc=unixodbc --enable-rlookups --enable-backends  --enable-overlays --enable-ndb=no --with-tls=openssl --enable-sql
2) make depend
3) make
4) make install

- Berkeley DB v4.6.21
http://download.oracle.com/berkeley-db/db-4.6.21.tar.gz

1) cd build_unix
2) ../dist/configure --prefix=/usr
2) make
3) make install

- Cyrus SASL v2.1.24rc1
http://ftp.andrew.cmu.edu/pub/cyrus-mail/cyrus-sasl-2.1.24rc1.tar.gz

1) ./configure --prefix=/usr
2) make
3) make install

- unixODBC v2.3.0
ftp://ftp.unixodbc.org/pub/unixODBC/unixODBC-2.3.0.tar.gz

1) ./configure --prefix=/usr
2) make
3) make install


